[
  {
    "startTime": 9.42,
    "endTime": 12.799,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.799,
    "endTime": 14.96,
    "text": "this is an equipment graveyard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.96,
    "endTime": 17.279,
    "text": "it's a typical final resting place for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.279,
    "endTime": 19.279,
    "text": "medical equipment from hospitals in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.279,
    "endTime": 20.56,
    "text": "africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.56,
    "endTime": 23.439,
    "text": "now why is this most of the medical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.439,
    "endTime": 25.279,
    "text": "devices used in africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.279,
    "endTime": 28.4,
    "text": "are imported and quite often they're not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.4,
    "endTime": 31.039,
    "text": "suitable for local conditions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.039,
    "endTime": 34.559,
    "text": "they may require trained staff that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.559,
    "endTime": 36.8,
    "text": "aren't available to operate and maintain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.8,
    "endTime": 39.6,
    "text": "and repair them they may not be able to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.6,
    "endTime": 40.32,
    "text": "withstand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.32,
    "endTime": 42.64,
    "text": "high temperatures and humidity and they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.64,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "usually require"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 45.92,
    "text": "a constant and reliable supply of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.92,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "electricity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 50.399,
    "text": "an example of a medical device that may"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.399,
    "endTime": 51.68,
    "text": "have ended up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.68,
    "endTime": 54.879,
    "text": "in an equipment graveyard at some point"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.879,
    "endTime": 57.36,
    "text": "is an ultrasound monitor to track the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.36,
    "endTime": 58.079,
    "text": "heart rate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.079,
    "endTime": 61.6,
    "text": "of unborn babies this is the standard of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.6,
    "endTime": 62.239,
    "text": "care"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.239,
    "endTime": 64.64,
    "text": "in rich countries in low resource"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.64,
    "endTime": 65.439,
    "text": "settings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.439,
    "endTime": 68.88,
    "text": "the standard of care is often a midwife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.88,
    "endTime": 70.72,
    "text": "listening to the baby's heart rate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.72,
    "endTime": 72.56,
    "text": "through a horn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.56,
    "endTime": 74.799,
    "text": "now this approach has been around for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.799,
    "endTime": 76.56,
    "text": "more than a century"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.56,
    "endTime": 78.799,
    "text": "it's very much dependent on the skill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.799,
    "endTime": 82.479,
    "text": "and the experience of the midwife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.479,
    "endTime": 85.759,
    "text": "two young inventors from uganda visited"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.759,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "an"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 88.64,
    "text": "antenatal clinic at a local hospital a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.64,
    "endTime": 89.759,
    "text": "few years ago"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.759,
    "endTime": 91.759,
    "text": "when they were students in information"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.759,
    "endTime": 93.36,
    "text": "technology"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.36,
    "endTime": 96.159,
    "text": "they noticed that quite often the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.159,
    "endTime": 98.159,
    "text": "midwife was not able to hear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.159,
    "endTime": 100.079,
    "text": "any heart rate when listening trying to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.079,
    "endTime": 102.56,
    "text": "listen to it through this horn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.56,
    "endTime": 105.92,
    "text": "so they invented their own fetal heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.92,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "rate monitor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 110.88,
    "text": "they adapted the horn and connected it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.88,
    "endTime": 112.64,
    "text": "to a smartphone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.64,
    "endTime": 115.28,
    "text": "an app on the smartphone records the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.28,
    "endTime": 116.079,
    "text": "heart rate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.079,
    "endTime": 118.64,
    "text": "analyzes it and provides the midwife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.64,
    "endTime": 120.159,
    "text": "with a range of information"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.159,
    "endTime": 123.439,
    "text": "on the status of the baby"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.439,
    "endTime": 127.68,
    "text": "these inventors are called aaron tushave"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.68,
    "endTime": 132.239,
    "text": "and joshua o'kello another inventor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.239,
    "endTime": 135.84,
    "text": "tender kai katsiga was working for an"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.84,
    "endTime": 139.2,
    "text": "ngo in botswana that manufactured"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.2,
    "endTime": 140.72,
    "text": "hearing aids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.72,
    "endTime": 144.48,
    "text": "now he noticed that these hearing aids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.48,
    "endTime": 146.879,
    "text": "needed batteries that needed replacement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.879,
    "endTime": 148.64,
    "text": "very often at a cost that was not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.64,
    "endTime": 149.599,
    "text": "affordable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.599,
    "endTime": 152.239,
    "text": "for most of the users that he knew now"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.239,
    "endTime": 153.84,
    "text": "in response"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.84,
    "endTime": 157.2,
    "text": "and being an engineer tendikai invented"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.2,
    "endTime": 159.68,
    "text": "a solar-powered battery charger with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.68,
    "endTime": 161.28,
    "text": "rechargeable batteries that could be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.28,
    "endTime": 163.44,
    "text": "used in these hearing aids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.44,
    "endTime": 166.319,
    "text": "he co-founded a company called"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.319,
    "endTime": 167.44,
    "text": "deathtronics"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.44,
    "endTime": 170.56,
    "text": "which now manufactures the solar ear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.56,
    "endTime": 172.879,
    "text": "which is a hearing aid powered by his"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.879,
    "endTime": 175.44,
    "text": "invention"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.76,
    "endTime": 178.8,
    "text": "my colleague sudesh sivarasu"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.8,
    "endTime": 181.599,
    "text": "invented a smart glove for people who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.599,
    "endTime": 183.68,
    "text": "have suffered from leprosy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.68,
    "endTime": 185.84,
    "text": "even though their disease may have been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.84,
    "endTime": 188.56,
    "text": "cured the resulting nerve damage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.56,
    "endTime": 190.239,
    "text": "will have left many of them without a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.239,
    "endTime": 192.48,
    "text": "sense of touch in their hands"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.48,
    "endTime": 195.84,
    "text": "this puts them at risk of injury"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.84,
    "endTime": 198.239,
    "text": "the glove has sensors to detect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.239,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "temperature and pressure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 203.68,
    "text": "and warn the user it effectively serves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.68,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "as an artificial sense of touch"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 209.12,
    "text": "and prevents injury sudesh invented this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.12,
    "endTime": 209.599,
    "text": "glove"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.599,
    "endTime": 212.64,
    "text": "after observing former leprosy patients"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.64,
    "endTime": 214.239,
    "text": "as they carried out their day-to-day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.239,
    "endTime": 217.04,
    "text": "activities and he learnt about the risks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.04,
    "endTime": 220.719,
    "text": "and the hazards in their environment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.68,
    "endTime": 223.92,
    "text": "now the inventors that i've mentioned"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.92,
    "endTime": 227.12,
    "text": "integrated engineering with healthcare"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.12,
    "endTime": 230.4,
    "text": "this is what biomedical engineers do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.4,
    "endTime": 232.799,
    "text": "at the university of cape town we run a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.799,
    "endTime": 234.319,
    "text": "course called health innovation and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.319,
    "endTime": 235.519,
    "text": "design"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.519,
    "endTime": 237.519,
    "text": "it's taken by many of our graduate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.519,
    "endTime": 240.159,
    "text": "students in biomedical engineering the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.159,
    "endTime": 241.599,
    "text": "aim of the course"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.599,
    "endTime": 243.84,
    "text": "is to introduce these students to the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.84,
    "endTime": 246.159,
    "text": "philosophy of the design world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.159,
    "endTime": 248.239,
    "text": "the students are encouraged to engage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.239,
    "endTime": 250.159,
    "text": "with communities as they search for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.159,
    "endTime": 252.959,
    "text": "solutions to health related problems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.959,
    "endTime": 254.72,
    "text": "one of the communities that we work with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.72,
    "endTime": 256.479,
    "text": "is a group of elderly people in cape"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.479,
    "endTime": 257.44,
    "text": "town"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.44,
    "endTime": 260.479,
    "text": "a recent class project had the task of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.479,
    "endTime": 262.56,
    "text": "addressing hearing loss in these elderly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.56,
    "endTime": 263.759,
    "text": "people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.759,
    "endTime": 265.36,
    "text": "the students many of them being"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.36,
    "endTime": 267.6,
    "text": "engineers set out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.6,
    "endTime": 269.68,
    "text": "believing that they would design a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.68,
    "endTime": 271.36,
    "text": "better hearing aid"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.36,
    "endTime": 273.36,
    "text": "they spent time with the elderly chatted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.36,
    "endTime": 275.04,
    "text": "to their healthcare providers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.04,
    "endTime": 278.32,
    "text": "and their caregivers they soon realized"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.32,
    "endTime": 278.639,
    "text": "that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.639,
    "endTime": 280.84,
    "text": "actually adequate hearing aids already"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.84,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "existed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 284.32,
    "text": "but many of the elderly who needed them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.32,
    "endTime": 286.08,
    "text": "and had access to them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.08,
    "endTime": 288.8,
    "text": "didn't have them and many of those who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.8,
    "endTime": 290.0,
    "text": "had hearing aids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.0,
    "endTime": 294.24,
    "text": "wouldn't wear them the students realized"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.24,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "that many of these elderly people were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 298.08,
    "text": "in denial of their hearing loss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.08,
    "endTime": 299.68,
    "text": "there's a stigma attached to wearing a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.68,
    "endTime": 301.6,
    "text": "hearing aid"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.6,
    "endTime": 303.199,
    "text": "they also discovered that the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.199,
    "endTime": 305.12,
    "text": "environment in which these elderly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.12,
    "endTime": 306.32,
    "text": "people lived"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.32,
    "endTime": 308.479,
    "text": "did not accommodate their hearing loss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.479,
    "endTime": 309.6,
    "text": "for example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.6,
    "endTime": 312.24,
    "text": "their homes and then community centre"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.24,
    "endTime": 314.08,
    "text": "were filled with echoes that interfered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.08,
    "endTime": 315.919,
    "text": "with their hearing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.919,
    "endTime": 319.039,
    "text": "so instead of developing and designing a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.039,
    "endTime": 320.96,
    "text": "new and better hearing aid"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.96,
    "endTime": 322.56,
    "text": "the student did an audit of the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.56,
    "endTime": 325.12,
    "text": "environment with a view to improving the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.12,
    "endTime": 327.039,
    "text": "acoustics"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.039,
    "endTime": 329.44,
    "text": "they also devised a campaign to raise"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.44,
    "endTime": 330.96,
    "text": "awareness of hearing loss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.96,
    "endTime": 333.12,
    "text": "and to counter the stigma attached to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.12,
    "endTime": 335.44,
    "text": "wearing a hearing aid"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.44,
    "endTime": 337.199,
    "text": "now this often happens when one pays"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.199,
    "endTime": 338.88,
    "text": "attention to the user"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.88,
    "endTime": 341.36,
    "text": "in this case the elderly and their needs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.36,
    "endTime": 343.039,
    "text": "and their context"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.039,
    "endTime": 344.56,
    "text": "one often has to move away from the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.56,
    "endTime": 347.12,
    "text": "focus of technology and reformulate the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.12,
    "endTime": 348.72,
    "text": "problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.72,
    "endTime": 350.639,
    "text": "now this approach to understanding a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.639,
    "endTime": 352.8,
    "text": "problem through listening and engaging"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.8,
    "endTime": 356.0,
    "text": "is not new but it often isn't followed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.0,
    "endTime": 358.319,
    "text": "by engineers who are intent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.319,
    "endTime": 361.6,
    "text": "on developing technology"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.6,
    "endTime": 363.52,
    "text": "one of our students has a background in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.52,
    "endTime": 364.96,
    "text": "software engineering"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.96,
    "endTime": 367.12,
    "text": "he had often created products for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.12,
    "endTime": 369.28,
    "text": "clients that the client ultimately did"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.28,
    "endTime": 370.72,
    "text": "not like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.72,
    "endTime": 372.96,
    "text": "when a client would reject a product it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.96,
    "endTime": 374.88,
    "text": "was common at his company"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.88,
    "endTime": 377.44,
    "text": "to proclaim that the client just didn't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.44,
    "endTime": 379.36,
    "text": "know what they wanted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.36,
    "endTime": 381.52,
    "text": "having completed the course the student"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.52,
    "endTime": 382.8,
    "text": "fed back to us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.8,
    "endTime": 385.039,
    "text": "that he now realized that it was he who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.039,
    "endTime": 388.16,
    "text": "hadn't understood what the client wanted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.16,
    "endTime": 390.639,
    "text": "another student student gave us feedback"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.639,
    "endTime": 392.479,
    "text": "that she had learned to design with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.479,
    "endTime": 393.199,
    "text": "empathy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.199,
    "endTime": 395.199,
    "text": "as opposed to designing for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.199,
    "endTime": 396.8,
    "text": "functionality which is what our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.8,
    "endTime": 399.6,
    "text": "engineering education had taught her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.6,
    "endTime": 401.6,
    "text": "so what all of this illustrates us that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.6,
    "endTime": 403.84,
    "text": "is that we often blinded to real needs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.84,
    "endTime": 406.4,
    "text": "in our pursuit of technology but we need"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.4,
    "endTime": 407.36,
    "text": "technology"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.36,
    "endTime": 409.12,
    "text": "we need hearing aids we need fetal heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.12,
    "endTime": 411.28,
    "text": "rate monitors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.28,
    "endTime": 413.919,
    "text": "so how do we create more medical device"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.919,
    "endTime": 415.039,
    "text": "success stories"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.039,
    "endTime": 417.919,
    "text": "from africa how do we create more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.919,
    "endTime": 418.88,
